### Create Test (Admin)
POST {{baseUrl}}/tests
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "title": "Math Test - Level 1",
  "description": "Basic math skills",
  "questions": [
    {
      "content": "2 + 2 = ?",
      "answers": [
        { "text": "3", "score": 0 },
        { "text": "4", "score": 1 },
        { "text": "5", "score": 0 }
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "5 * 2 = ?",
      "answers": [
        { "text": "10", "score": 1 },
        { "text": "8", "score": 0 },
        { "text": "12", "score": 0 }
      ]
    }
  ]
}

### Get All Tests 
GET {{baseUrl}}/tests
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get Single Test (with questions & answers)
GET {{baseUrl}}/tests/{{testId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Assign Test to Child
POST {{baseUrl}}/tests/test-assignments
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "childId": "d8b8c672-2144-4f47-84f7-9571311f50f1",
  "testId": "1c26375e-a25c-4180-b82f-de69a6faabcd",
  "due_date": "2026-03-25"
}


### solve test
POST {{baseUrl}}/tests/test-results/submit
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "assignmentId": "e7268c93-1d44-463c-96f0-47b2fa3615f3",
  "answers": [
    {
      "questionId": "bed4aeaa-4d54-4f72-80b6-da02ffcf12be",
